  "name": "RPlog_An_Unlikely_Alliance",
  "title": "An Unlikely Alliance",
  "summary": "Over the blockaded Nar Shaddaa, Luke Skywalker volunteers to fly patrol from the New Republic corvette Audacity alongside the green Flight Cadet Doherty, while the Corporate Sector task force under Colonel Gren Delede shadows the system from the Strike Cruiser Authority. When Delede hails the X-wings, a cautious tightbeam exchange reveals both sides share a common enemy in the Sith Lord Tyler Damign (Malign), who is sowing chaos in the underworld and holding Delede's people hostage on the surface. Luke agrees to meet Delede and his fiancee, the embittered Twi'lek Lt. Twila Virda, aboard the Authority, coming alone. In the cleared hangar, Delede confesses the bargain he struck with Malign to save Twila and hands Luke a comm device that can contact Tyler directly, pledging his fleet to a strike against the Sith. Luke warns that Tyler may have foreseen the meeting but vows to rally the fleet, exchanging tactical intelligence and a wary alliance before departing.",
